description:
Tape for breast firming Bye Bra with silk pads on the nipples is a simple solution for fast and effective improvement of the female breasts without the need for surgical procedures or even a bra! Sticky bands work by lifting the breasts from the top, making Bye Bra the ideal solution for strapless blouses and without a covered back. The Bye Bra chest strap can also be worn under a bikini. Self-adhesive tapes are made of very thin and flexible film produced by 3M. The same type of film is used in hospitals and is dermatologically safe.
Recommendation: In case the size of the cup is in two sizes, we always recommend a larger size. In case it is too big - just remove or cut the unnecessary part with scissors.
The Bye Bra chest strap is available in 3 sizes: A-C, D-F and F +. All three sizes are available with silk nipple pads. EAN: 8717953077639

description: Bye Bra provides a new generation of belts with flexible ends that match any bra with two hooks. The strap on the back is a strap without a bra that pulls the bra so you can not see it. description:
The tapes are made of 3M glue, and the stripe sizes are 23 mm by 82 mm. They are much wider and longer than the average tape. This is a useful feature because this tape can stay on the body all night long compared to other thinner ones that do not last for so much time. The 3M adhesive has exceptional quality - it is gentle on both the skin and clothing. The protective layers between them ensure that the strips do not stick together before use. The combination of Bye Bra self-adhesive breast lift and tape prevents the frightening "nipple". The package has 30 strips, but due to their size, they can be cut in half and you can have up to 60 pieces.
Instructions: Before applying strips, make sure that the skin is dry and clean of any creams or moisturizing substances. First, choose a place on the skin to which you want to attach clothing. Then peel the backing paper from the inside of the strap and press the tape firmly against the skin. When the tape is in place, remove the backing paper from the outside surface and push the garment to it. Hold it in place for a few seconds before releasing. To remove the tape after use, simply peel it off. If it does not come easily - soak your clothes in warm soapy water and try again. Apply baby oil or similar product to the skin to speed up the process and try again. EAN: 8718801010952

description: The best currently available Toe Bra nipples. They are made of Henkel glue and are tested by SGS. These silicone nipple pads in the shape of flowers are perfect for everyday wear. They hide the protrusion of the nipples and protect the nipples, regardless of whether you wear a bra or not. Silicone nipple pads are perfect under dresses, gala clothes, strapless dresses. They are wider and thicker than silk overlays. On our site you can choose from two types - silk or silicone pads. Both types work great, but each type is best suited for a particular purpose. We recommend silicone nipple pads if you have a lot of clothes rubbing or have large and sensitive envelopes, because the silicone nipple is larger than its silk counterpart and has a lower adhesive strength. Both nipple covers will stay in place, despite the sweat; however, if you sweat a lot, we recommend using silk covers because they have a stronger adhesive and are therefore better than silicone covers. The package contains four pairs of overlays. EAN: 8718801010044

description: The best currently available Toe Bra nipples. They are made of Henkel glue and are tested by SGS. These silk flower-shaped nipples are perfect for everyday wear. They hide the protrusion of the nipples and protect the nipples, regardless of whether you wear a bra or not. Silk nipples are perfect for dresses, gala clothes, strapless dresses. On our site you can choose from two types - silk or silicone pads. Both types work great, but each type is best suited for a particular purpose. We recommend silicone nipple pads if you have a lot of clothes rubbing or have large and sensitive envelopes, because the silicone nipple is larger than its silk counterpart and has a lower adhesive strength.
